-------------------------------------------------------
	InitScript
-Selects what scripts you want to run
-Create dir /opt/scripts
-Can be manipulated to run any script wanted
-Ex.	0)All
	1)One
	2)Two
	3)Three
-------------------------------------------------------
	SSH Config
-Save inital config to sshd_config.bak to /opt/scripts
-remove and purge openssh-server
-reinstall openssh-server
-delete sshd_config
-Download presecured config to sshd_config
-restart ssh service
-------------------------------------------------------
